@baseURL = http://localhost:3000

### Prueba health
GET {{baseURL}}/health

### Registrar usuario
POST {{baseURL}}/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "jaime10@example.com",
    "password": "Password.123"
}

