}

### Subir logo de la compañía
PATCH {{baseURL}}/api/user/logo
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJfaWQiOiI2OWQzOGNiMzMwY2NlZmZjNGZiZDZhOWIiLCJyb2xlIjoiYWRtaW4iLCJpYXQiOjE3NzU1MDA4MjAsImV4cCI6MTc3NTUwMTcyMH0.mGJKy_341Fm5_Is0Rgl81ZyEOgITLNCLpYYnoZN3T0k
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="logo"; filename="logo.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./logo1.jpg
--boundary--

